001package xjtlu.cpt111.assignment.quiz.model;
002
003/**
004 * Enumeration for representing the difficulty of a question.
005 * 
006 * @author H.-P. Lam, Xi'an Jiaotong-Liverpool University (XJTLU)
007 * @since 2024.09.10
008 * @since version 0.0.1
009 * @version Last modified: 2024.09.10
010 */
011public enum Difficulty {
012        /**
013         * EASY indicates that the question is an easy/simple question
014         */
015        EASY,
016
017        /**
018         * MEDIUM indicates that the question is a question with medium difficulty
019         */
020        MEDIUM,
021
022        /**
023         * HARD indicates that the question is a hard question
024         */
025        HARD,
026
027        /**
028         * VERY_HARD indicates that the question is a very hard question
029         */
030        VERY_HARD
031}
